<br>
In regards to the common speech. I believe it would make more sense if languages were set up along more racial lines than by where you live. Several ideas come to me on this matter:<br>
<br>
All like races (Erudite, Human, Barbarian,Halfelf;Woodelf, Highelf,Halfelf; Gnomes, Halflings, Dwarves; Trolls and Ogres)  could have a common language or , at the very least have a slight proficiancy for (like an avergage skill in one another's native tongues)<br>
I know this leaves out Iksar and Darkelf, as such, a language based on the deity you worship could be implemented and since the alliance of the Darkelves, Ogres and Trolls are in the game, an average proficiancy in one another's language would be suitable here as well. As far as Iksar are concerned a relationship with other worshipers of <br>
Cazic-Thule would suffice.<br>
<br>
Donagall McFlurry<br>
Barbarian Necromancer of Melee<br>
Morell-Thule<br>
