<br>
For example Crystal Caverns a lvl 35-45 zone, yesterday there were 10 people 50+ in that zone all wiping away orcs, spiders and leeches. A lvl 1 could walk around that cave without being afraid she would die.<br>
<br>
Personally I would also choose such a new server for those changes over the fact it would be called Roleplaying. To get a real roleplaying server many more changes have to be made, pvp-unconsious, pvp-kill, quest redesigns, remove camp spots, more diety items and diety based spells (you could not heal some people with contradict diety), player consider system (paladin considering a shadow knight would get 'aggressive'-con), alignment system with penalties for not following you alignment (a paladin gone bad would lose it's spells etc.), more all/all cloths items flagpoles horses carts etc,etc,etc,...<br>
<br>
Ofcourse you can roleplay everywhere and in any game, but it is the encouragement that is needed to have more and more people roleplay and have it as the only playstyle on a server. When a RP server will come, their should also come a Race Server, a Kewl Dude Server, a Hardcore Server, etc, for all the playstyles.<br>
<br>
